This is a .net WPF application that uses a Kinect 360 sensor with 1.7 kinect SDK.

Sensor should be at belly height circa 2-3 meters from player.  
Player should stay on the left side of the screen.
  
To play Press Start
  Choose your players color using the RGB sliders
  
To select level Vocal command : "level one" "level two" "level three"
To start level hit the circle with the RightHand.

Everytime you bounce the "bullet" back to the enemy and it hits the enemy the score goes up.

To end a level just select a new level.


